sql:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM title t, movie_companies mc, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year  =  1998 AND mc.company_id  >  11147 AND mk.keyword_id  >  7663
